    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034760/extras/42be89be7148e33f00bc4fcdeaf4de36.poster.avif?t=1771431157\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034760/extras/42be89be7148e33f00bc4fcdeaf4de36.webm?t=1771431157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034760/extras/42be89be7148e33f00bc4fcdeaf4de36.mp4?t=1771431157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world has fallen into silence. The wind is gone. In <strong>STONEFEATHER</strong>,  you fly as a stone-born bird drawn to the last echoes of the breeze. Restore what was lost, and let hope carry you across a mystical journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034760/extras/7ec9b0c22e16bc92b4648a7523ee9454.poster.avif?t=1771431157\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034760/extras/7ec9b0c22e16bc92b4648a7523ee9454.webm?t=1771431157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034760/extras/7ec9b0c22e16bc92b4648a7523ee9454.mp4?t=1771431157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FLY WITH FLOW</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A flight system built for precision and control: dive to build speed, sweep into wide arcs, and carve smooth lines through the air. <strong>Your wings are your compass. Movement is expression, exploration, and mastery</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034760/extras/cdc4a50592dd679a4ab05499d70e44d1.poster.avif?t=1771431157\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034760/extras/cdc4a50592dd679a4ab05499d70e44d1.webm?t=1771431157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034760/extras/cdc4a50592dd679a4ab05499d70e44d1.mp4?t=1771431157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>RESTORE THE WIND</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find the scattered <strong>Essences of Zefir</strong> and release the breath trapped in stone. Each awakening brings back wind currents, including updrafts, and gusts that let you travel through the world with greater freedom and speed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034760/extras/937ecfa904b6a530d9b3700a0793ced4.poster.avif?t=1771431157\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034760/extras/937ecfa904b6a530d9b3700a0793ced4.webm?t=1771431157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034760/extras/937ecfa904b6a530d9b3700a0793ced4.mp4?t=1771431157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>EXPLORE SILENT RUINS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Journey through a seamless, handcrafted <strong>open world</strong> shaped around flight and vertical landmarks. Navigate by sight and instinct, discover hidden spaces among the ruins, and <strong>explore at your own pace</strong>. A wholesome sense of wonder walks with you, with touches of gentle melancholy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034760/extras/4527d52e3d0bdced0ec6e30bad5c4202.poster.avif?t=1771431157\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034760/extras/4527d52e3d0bdced0ec6e30bad5c4202.webm?t=1771431157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034760/extras/4527d52e3d0bdced0ec6e30bad5c4202.mp4?t=1771431157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FOLLOW THE ECHO</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let the Elder guide you. Gather fragments, read the world’s symbols, and piece together what bound the wind and why you were called to set it free.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034760/extras/0ecb3d1b68e0b40340c31b63d898ad7d.poster.avif?t=1771431157\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034760/extras/0ecb3d1b68e0b40340c31b63d898ad7d.webm?t=1771431157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034760/extras/0ecb3d1b68e0b40340c31b63d898ad7d.mp4?t=1771431157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FLIGHT TRIALS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect hidden finds as you fly through rings and chase optional aerial routes across the world. These gentle trials and discoveries reward curiosity and help you fly higher.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
